info.title: Qwen Text Embedding v4 - AI/ML API
info.description: Qwen Text Embedding v4 is a next-generation universal embedding model that supports over 100 languages and configurable embedding dimensions from 64 to 2048. It is designed for high-quality text representations for search, retrieval, and semantic similarity tasks.
